your Grandpa Hokage.

176
00:12:46,057 --> 00:12:48,351
My name is Konohamaru.

177
00:12:49,102 --> 00:12:51,438
It was Grandpa who gave me
that name.

178
00:12:52,147 --> 00:12:53,940
He named me after our village.

179
00:12:56,109 --> 00:12:59,696
