that easily, you know.

189
00:13:34,564 --> 00:13:35,565
What?!

190
00:13:36,650 --> 00:13:38,318
It's not that simple.

191
00:13:40,111 --> 00:13:43,740
If you're really serious about gaining
the title of Lord Hokage...

192
00:13:44,824 --> 00:13:45,867
What?

193
00:13:47,953 --> 00:13:50,622
You'll have to beat me first!

194
00:14:05,637 --> 00:14:09,432
Lord Hokage!
I've been looking for you.

195
00:14:09,933 --> 00:14:11,059
Iruka.

196
00:14:11,643 --> 00:14:15,438
Did Naruto re-submit
his Ninja Registration Form?

197
00:14:15,522 --> 00:14:16,523
Yes.

198
00:14:16,606 --> 00:14:20,151
When I lectured to him the other night
at the ramen stand,

199
00:14:20,235 --> 00:14:24,781
he said he will make everyone accept him
now that he's a Ninja.

200
00:14:24,864 --> 00:14:26,741
He's been happy since then.

201
00:14:32,789 --> 00:14:37,043
It might not be easy for Naruto
to realize that dream.

202
00:14:37,127 --> 00:14:38,169
Huh?

203
00:14:39,087 --> 00:14:41,131
As you well know,

204
00:14:41,214 --> 00:14:46,720
only the villagers who fought
the Nine-Tailed Fox Spirit 12 years ago

205
00:14:46,803 --> 00:14:51,224
know that the monster is sealed
inside Naruto.

206
00:14:52,058 --> 00:14:55,687
I ruled that no one shall speak
about that incident.

207
00:14:55,770 --> 00:14:59,733
