who have broken this rule.

208
00:15:00,483 --> 00:15:04,279
Now our children know nothing about it.

209
00:15:04,362 --> 00:15:07,657
That is the only positive
development for Naruto.

210
00:15:07,741 --> 00:15:13,496
Before the Fourth Hokage trapped
the monster and died,

211
00:15:13,580 --> 00:15:16,499
his last wish was for the villagers
to regard Naruto as a hero.

212
00:15:16,583 --> 00:15:17,626
A hero?

213
00:15:18,752 --> 00:15:22,964
The Fourth Hokage sealed the monster
into the navel of a newborn baby

214
00:15:23,048 --> 00:15:25,133
whose umbilical cord
had just been cut.

215
00:15:25,216 --> 00:15:28,345
As the receptacle
for the Nine-Tailed Fox Spirit,

216
00:15:28,428 --> 00:15:31,306
Naruto saved the village.

217
00:15:31,389 --> 00:15:36,561
Unfortunately, the other villagers
don't see him like that.

218
00:15:37,145 --> 00:15:42,025
Some even say that Naruto is
the Nine-Tailed Fox Spirit himself.

219
00:15:42,776 --> 00:15:45,612
Little by little, that attitude

220
00:15:45,695 --> 00:15:50,742
has been
passed down to their own children.

221
00:15:52,869 --> 00:15:55,580
Iruka.
Do you know?

222
00:15:56,081 --> 00:15:57,499
What, sir?

223
00:15:57,582 --> 00:16:02,337
