we have to go now.

230
00:16:32,409 --> 00:16:33,702
No way!

231
00:16:33,785 --> 00:16:37,080
I want to beat Grandpa right now
so I can win the title of Lord Hokage!

232
00:16:38,081 --> 00:16:39,124
