will never work on me!

242
00:17:11,531 --> 00:17:17,078
Honorable Grandson!
That rascal will only make you an imbecile!

243
00:17:18,163 --> 00:17:20,165
Stick with me and...

244
00:17:20,248 --> 00:17:23,251
you will gain a shortcut
towards becoming the Fifth Hokage.

245
00:17:23,334 --> 00:17:25,170
C'mon, let's go!

246
00:17:25,253 --> 00:17:26,254
