I want to be recognized by everybody!

262
00:19:02,725 --> 00:19:04,519
But I keep failing.

263
00:19:05,311 --> 00:19:06,896
You think it's that easy?

264
00:19:06,980 --> 00:19:08,356
Huh?

265
00:19:08,439 --> 00:19:11,901
It's given only to the greatest Ninja
in the village.

266
00:19:11,985 --> 00:19:14,863
Everybody must learn to believe in you.

267
00:19:17,407 --> 00:19:20,243
I've been through a lot already.

268
00:19:20,827 --> 00:19:23,246
It's been one struggle after another.

269
00:19:24,289 --> 00:19:28,459
But after all that,
I found someone who accepts me.

270
00:19:29,210 --> 00:19:31,796
I had to go through a lot...
Just for one person.

271
00:19:33,256 --> 00:19:35,592
You had better push yourself.

272
00:19:35,675 --> 00:19:36,676
For what?

273
00:19:38,511 --> 00:19:43,641
The path of getting the title,
Lord Hokage, is a brutal one.

274
00:19:52,483 --> 00:19:55,570
There's no such thing as a shortcut.

275
00:20:00,408 --> 00:20:02,952
If you're really serious about
attaining the title of Lord Hokage

276
00:20:03,494 --> 00:20:05,622
You'll have to beat me first.

277
00:20:09,500 --> 00:20:13,004
Who do you think you are,
lecturing me like that?

278
00:20:14,297 --> 00:20:16,966
I won't be your apprentice anymore.

279
00:20:21,763 --> 00:20:25,016
From now on, you're my rival.

280
00:20:29,437 --> 00:20:33,983
Unfortunately for you,
tomorrow I graduate from the Ninja Academy.

281
00:20:34,484 --> 00:20:40,406
Still, I'll consider you an equal someday
when we fight for the title of Lord Hokage.

282
00:20:41,908 --> 00:20:45,995
Let's look forward to that, Konohamaru.

283
00:21:09,936 --> 00:21:15,692
You still have a long way to go
to become a real Ninja.

284
00:22:52,830 --> 00:22:56,751
Aaah! Why do I have to be in
the same group with Sasuke?

285
00:22:56,834 --> 00:22:58,586
The guy I hate the most?

286
00:22:58,669 --> 00:23:00,379
Sakura keeps saying
"Sasuke Sasuke Sasuke!"

287
00:23:00,463 --> 00:23:02,048
and doesn't even
pay attention to me!

288
00:23:02,131 --> 00:23:07,136
It makes me so mad!
I got it! I'm going to pull one on him!

289
00:23:07,220 --> 00:23:10,723
I'm not gonna let him be so cool
in front of Sakura!

290
00:23:11,390 --> 00:23:14,060
Next Episode:
"Sasuke and Sakura: Friends or Foes?"

291
00:23:14,143 --> 00:23:17,105
Watch my outstanding performance!

